Package org.cougaar.core.wp.bootstrap

Interface Summary
AdvertiseService This service is used by advertisers to listen for local agent bind/unbind changes.
AdvertiseService.Client  
BootstrapService This service is used by the client's server selection to start/stop the discovery components.
BundleService This service provides Bundles for local agents bound in the LeaseManager.
BundleService.Client  
ConfigService This service provides the initial Bundle configuration.
ConfigService.Client  
DiscoveryService This service is used by discovery pollers to listen for start/stop requests and pass their findings to the cache.
DiscoveryService.Client  
EnsureIsFoundService This service is used by the peer manager to ensure that server peers are found by the discovery bootstrapper.
HintService This service is provided by the CacheManager to bootstrap discovered Bundles into the local cache.
PeersService This service is used by servers to locate theirs peers, which is required for replication.
PeersService.Client  
ServersService This service is used by the SelectManager to list potental servers.
ServersService.Client  
ServiceFinder.Callback  
 

Class Summary
AdvertiseBase This component is a base class for (server) bootstrap advertisers.
AdvertiseManager This component runs in white pages servers to advertise locally-bound Bundles from the LeaseManager through the advertisers (rmi, http, multicast, etc).
Bundle Bootstrap data for a single agent, including its AddressEntrys.
BundleDecoder Decode Bundles and Certs from encoded text.
BundleEncoder Encode Bundles and Certs to encoded text.
ConfigManager This component provides the ConfigService that loads the static ConfigReader contents.
ConfigReader This utility class reads "-Dorg.cougaar.name.server" system properties and the "alpreg.ini" for bootstrap Bundles provided by the ConfigService.
DiscoveryBase This component is a base class for (client) bootstrap discoverers.
DiscoveryBase.Config config options
DiscoveryManager This component advertises the BootstrapService, which starts/stops the discovery pollers to find bootstrap Bundles and copy them into the CacheManager's HintService.
EnsureIsFoundManager This component advertises the EnsureIsFoundService, which allows servers to ensures that their peers are reachable.
PeersManager This component provides the PeersService, to tell the server about their peer servers.
ServiceFinder A utility class to hide late-binding Service lookups.
Util Bootstrap utility methods.
